				<p>thanks for being helpful and informative. I'm still confused though. Can I consider in the aforementioned example the walls as landmarks? I'm still confused because I've seen some videos in which there are some white circles which are recognized by the robot to determine its place. What the difference between the white circles and the walls?</p>
